narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes. It's a good continuation of your Russian studies.
Take it if you're into L5 Russian. It's less work than earlier levels and Constantine is great.
Take Russian 150 with Professor Muravnik. He teaches the class so well; it would be a shame to miss out on this class.

Take it if you are willing to put in the work. Falling behind does NOT feel good. The oral exams are difficult and you should prepare for them well in advance! Really great course, though-- Kostya is amazing.
